<Link id="l00137" /><CodeLine lineNumber="137"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// of the fact that all instructions are aligned to addresses of size</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00138" /><CodeLine lineNumber="138"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 2, so bit 0 of an address is always 0 This gives us another bit</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00139" /><CodeLine lineNumber="139"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// of precision.</span></CodeLine>
